sentences.sentence: To customize the artificial humeral head according to the upwards requirement.
sentences.translation: 按以上要求定制个体化的人工肱骨头。

sentences.sentence: Objective To analyze the reasons and treatment of nonunion of humeral shaft fracture.
sentences.translation: 目的探讨肱骨干骨折术后不愈合的原因及治疗方法。

sentences.sentence: Objective To explore the effect of the treatment of humeral intramedullary nail fracture healing.
sentences.translation: 目的探讨带锁髓内钉治疗肱骨骨折不愈合的疗效。
